      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "主数据流\n\n用户操作\n  → Features / Components\n  → Zustand Store\n  → Domain（plan / stream）\n  → agentRuntime.streamExecution\n      ├─ 有 API → Nest /executions/stream\n      ├─ 有 Key → OpenAI 兼容 LLM\n      └─ 否则 → Mock SSE\n  → Store 增量更新\n  → UI 流式渲染（Artifact / Trace）\n\n持久化旁路\nStore → persistenceApi\n  → Nest → SQLite\n  （离线 → localStorage）\n\n产品能力链\nPortal → Workspace\n  → Prompt / Skill / Workflow\n  → Agent\n  → Memory / KB / Tool\n  → LLM",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "主数据流\n\n用户操作\n  → Features / Components\n  → Zustand Store\n  → Domain（plan / stream）\n  → agentRuntime.streamExecution\n      ├─ 有 API → Nest /executions/stream\n      ├─ 有 Key → OpenAI 兼容 LLM\n      └─ 否则 → Mock SSE\n  → Store 增量更新\n  → UI 流式渲染（Artifact / Trace）\n\n持久化旁路\nStore → persistenceApi\n  → Nest → SQLite\n  （离线 → localStorage）\n\n产品能力链\nPortal → Workspace\n  → Prompt / Skill / Workflow\n  → Agent\n  → Memory / KB / Tool\n  → LLM",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
